title: Heavenly Demon Cultivation Simulation
summary: Heavenly Demon Cultivation Simulation Cultivation of Heaven, 천마육성 Murim RPG Simulation Summary: A group of scouts have been assigned to the area of the Mount Hua Sect by their great leader, ‘The Mantis’. The protagonist ‘Seol Hui’ faces the Hua Sect Master ‘Goo Jong Myung,’ and falls in mortal danger. A status windows then pops up and made him return to the time before he accepted the scouting mission. Once he receives the same scouting mission that left him dead, Seol Hui struggles to change the unavoidable reality. A status window that appears every crisis. Choices with uncertain future. The story of Seol Hui as he tries to find the best decision in his world mingled with life and death.
